{ % vim: set ft=djot : % }

`djotfmt` test wrapping at various inline element boundaries.

* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *

Test wrapping between a span and its attribute: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee
ffff gggg [highlighted]{ .big .red } word after.

Test wrapping inside a span attribute: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff
gggg hhhh [highlighted]{ .class1 .class2 .class3 .class4 .class5 } word
after.

Test wrapping between link text and url: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff
gggg hhhh iiii [link text](http://example.com/very/long/url/path) word
after.

Test wrapping between link text and ref: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff
gggg hhhh iiii [link text][ref label] word after.

Test wrapping between image and url: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg
hhhh iiii jjjj ![alt text](image.png) word after.

Test wrapping at emphasis boundary: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg
hhhh iiii jjjj kkkk {_emphasized text_} word after.

Test wrapping at strong boundary: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg
hhhh iiii jjjj kkkk {*strong text*} word after.

Test wrapping at mark boundary: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg hhhh
iiii jjjj kkkk {=marked text=} word after.

Test wrapping at insert boundary: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg
hhhh iiii jjjj kkkk {+inserted text+} word after.

Test wrapping at delete boundary: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg
hhhh iiii jjjj kkkk {-deleted text-} word after.

Test wrapping at subscript boundary: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg
hhhh iiii jjjj kkkk H{~two~}O compound after.

Test wrapping at superscript boundary: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff
gggg hhhh iiii jjjj kkkk E=mc{^two^} formula after.

Test wrapping at verbatim boundary: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg
hhhh iiii jjjj kkkk `code span content` word after.

Test wrapping at math boundary: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg hhhh
iiii jjjj kkkk $`e=mc^2` word after.

Test wrapping at raw inline boundary: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg
hhhh iiii jjjj `<br>`{=html} word after.

Test wrapping at footnote ref boundary: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff
gggg hhhh iiii jjjj kkkk text[^note1] word after.

Test wrapping at symbol boundary: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg
hhhh iiii jjjj kkkk reaction:+1: word after.

Test wrapping at smart punctuation: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg
hhhh iiii jjjj kkkk {"Hello world."} word after.

Test wrapping at em-dash: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg hhhh iiii
jjjj kkkk llll---mmm nnnn oooo pppp qqqq.

Test wrapping at ellipsis: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg hhhh iiii
jjjj kkkk llll...mmm nnnn oooo pppp qqqq.

Test wrapping with nested inline elements: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff
gggg hhhh iiii jjjj [{*strong inside*} link](http://example.com) word
after.

Test wrapping with standalone comment attribute: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd
eeee ffff gggg hhhh iiii jjjj { % a comment here % } word after.

Test wrapping at nonbreaking space: aaaa bbbb cccc dddd eeee ffff gggg
hhhh iiii jjjj kkkk mmm\ nnn word after.
